Uses of Class
org.oucs.oxpoints.timedim.TimeSpan

Packages that use TimeSpan
org.oucs.oxpoints.entities OxPointsEntitys are java representations of objects from the OxPoints ontology. 
org.oucs.oxpoints.entities.time While OxPointsEntitys are representation of OxPoints objects at a specific point in time, OxPointsTimeBasedEntity represent an OxPoints object over its lifespan. 
org.oucs.oxpoints.model Contains the classes implementing the data model. 
org.oucs.oxpoints.model.events OxPointsEvents are used to inform interested parties of changes in an OxPoints model. 
org.oucs.oxpoints.test.classes Contains various unit tests to test the functionality of the OxPoints system. 
org.oucs.oxpoints.timedim Contains classes that allow you to work with time based data. 
org.oucs.oxpoints.timedim.index Contains an interface and implementations of an index for time bound named graphs.
